# apps/<name>/public/_headers  → copied by Vite to dist/_headers, served by Cloudflare Pages.
# Production COOP/COEP so SharedArrayBuffer / threaded ONNX Runtime works.
# Vite's server.headers only cover the DEV server — this is the production equivalent.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-origin
